Class FirehoseService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.symphonyoss.client.services.FirehoseService

  • public class FirehoseService
extends Object
    [Experimental] Implementation of firehose for a given POD. Is equivalent to the MessageService, but broader coverage. Created by Frank Tarsillo on 5/15/2016.
